Another ENSO index is the Oceanic Niño Index (ONI) 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "NOAAa"

\end_inset

.
 The ONI measures monthly SST values in the tropical Pacific Ocean.
 The measurements take place in the region from 5 
